## Coroutine 基礎

### 啟動
```kotlin
import kotlinx.coroutines.*

fun main() = runBlocking {
    launch {
        delay(1000)
        println("World")
    }
    println("Hello")
}
// 印：Hello, World（順序）
```

### Suspend
```kotlin
suspend fun fetchUser(id: String): User {
    delay(1000)  // 非阻塞
    return User(...)
}

// 用
val user = fetchUser("u123")
```

### Scope
```kotlin
// GlobalScope（不建議）
GlobalScope.launch { ... }

// CoroutineScope（推薦）
val scope = CoroutineScope(Dispatchers.IO)
scope.launch { ... }

// ViewModelScope（Android）
viewModelScope.launch { ... }
```

## Flow（reactive stream）

```kotlin
fun userFlow(): Flow<User> = flow {
    while (true) {
        val user = fetchUser()
        emit(user)
        delay(5000)
    }
}

// 收
userFlow().collect { user ->
    println(user)
}
```

### StateFlow（UI state）
```kotlin
class UserViewModel : ViewModel() {
    private val _user = MutableStateFlow<User?>(null)
    val user: StateFlow<User?> = _user

    fun load(id: String) = viewModelScope.launch {
        _user.value = api.getUser(id)
    }
}

// Compose
val user by viewModel.user.collectAsState()
```

### SharedFlow（events）
```kotlin
private val _events = MutableSharedFlow<String>()
val events: SharedFlow<String> = _events

// 發
_events.emit("Login success")
```

## Structured Concurrency

### supervisorScope
其中一個 fail 不影響其他：
```kotlin
supervisorScope {
    launch { task1() }
    launch { task2() }  // task1 fail、task2 仍跑
}
```

### withContext（切 thread）
```kotlin
suspend fun loadData() = withContext(Dispatchers.IO) {
    db.query(...)  // IO thread
}
```

## 心法
- Coroutine 取代 Thread / Callback
- viewModelScope 自動 cancel
- Flow > LiveData（現代）
- StateFlow for UI、SharedFlow for events

